Configuration (config/)
System Configuration (YAML)
yaml
default_parameters:
  initial_state_A: 0.3
  historical_horizon: 200
  aufhebung_threshold: 0.85
  volatility_factor: 0.03
  
stages:
  coherence_threshold: 0.15
  anomaly_threshold: 0.35
  paradox_threshold: 0.7
Visualization Configuration
yaml
colors:
  stage_0: "#2E8B57"    # Coherence
  stage_6: "#FF00FF"    # Paradoxical Transcendence
  stage_7: "#00FFFF"    # False Stability
  
plot_settings:
  figure_size: [16, 12]
  dpi: 150
  style: "seaborn-whitegrid"
