ğŸ”§ Installation & Setup
Minimal Installation
bash
git clone https://github.com/kxenopoulou/epistemology-of-logic
cd epistemology-of-logic
pip install -r requirements.txt
Development Installation
bash
git clone https://github.com/kxenopoulou/epistemology-of-logic
cd epistemology-of-logic
pip install -e .[dev]
pre-commit install
Docker Installation
bash
docker build -t xenopoulos-system .
docker run -p 8888:8888 xenopoulos-system
